.

1. *Novi* novčanik je bio skup, ali zadovoljan sam odabirom. (The new wallet was expensive, but I'm happy with my choice.)
2. Moja majka je dobila *novi* automobil pre neki dan. (My mom got a new car the other day.)
3. Svi smo se radovali kada je deci stigao *novi* igrački kompjuter. (We were all excited when the kids got a new toy computer.)
4. Moj prijatelj je potrošio ogroman novac na *nove* čizme. (My friend spent a lot of money on new boots.)
5. Poznanik mi je poklonio *novu* knjigu o istoriji. (My acquaintance gave me a new book about history.)